commentAnnotations.text: For Japan only: The following events will be handled as 'deemed serious for any other reason': AEs which possibly lead to disability will be reported as SAEs.
Cancers of new histology and exacerbations of existing cancer must be reported as a serious event regardless of the duration between discontinuation of the drug and the occurrence of the cancer.
The investigator must document the reason why patient not on target dose per local guidelines.
